# Compendiums are not part of this module. Blacksmith bundles no packs: they are not
# declared in module.json and are not in the release zip. Users select their own
# compendiums in settings. This repo lives inside a live Foundry install, so the
# folder still exists on disk and Foundry churns it every run — git just ignores it.
